data.text:
Biography[]

Danny Lux came from San Fernando Valley attended Sepulveda Jr. High through the highly gifted magnet later graduating from Granada Hills High School.

Composing Credits[]

Sliders, Million Dollar Mysteries, Crisis Center, Profiler, and Boston Legal. My Name Is Earl (with Mark Leggett), Boston Legal, Grey's Anatomy, Karen Sisco, Hack, Ally McBeal, Boston Public, NYPD Blue, John Doe, Sabrina, the Teenage Witch, The Good Wife, Melrose Place, Dawson's Creek, Suits, Magic's Biggest Secrets Finally Revealed, Robotica, Mistresses, and Manifest.]

[]
